  Source:
    Title: Srimad Bhagavatam
    Locus: XI xx
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Charity=Mercy
---
He who realizes the Lord God. the Atman, the one existence, the Self of the
universe, neither praises nor dispraises any man. Like the sun shining
impartially upon all things, he looks with an equal eye upon all beings. He
moves about in the world a free soul, released from all attachment.
